  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exosuit Appearance Override</span>.<br><br>Replaces the standard Jetpack combustion chamber with a plasma engine. During flight, the exhaust nozzles release dazzling clouds of ionized matter.<br><br>Transform the appearance of your Exosuit at an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Appearance Modifier</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">套装外观</span>。<br><br>使用等离子引擎替换标准的喷气背包燃烧室。飞行期间，排气喷口将施放让人眼花缭乱的离子物质云团。<br><br>可以在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外观修改器</span>使用以更改你的套装外观。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "特殊的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">強化套裝外觀覆寫</span>。<br><br>以電漿引擎替代標準噴射背包壓縮艙。飛行時，排氣噴嘴會釋放搶眼的離子化物質團。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外觀改造器</span>改變你的強化套裝外觀。"
  },
